  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>A spark with an opinion. Cinder Motes drift toward combustible material and burn it. Their combat contribution is negligible; their utility is specific and narrow. A summoner who needs a torch lit, a rope burned through, or a door set alight if it opens will find them adequate. A summoner who tries to use one as a fighter has misjudged what they called.</p>"
